<seg id="750">& dot; algorithm, the standard for directional graphs. it produces hierarchical or layered representations of directional graphs. the algorithm places the edges in the same direction (from top to bottom or from left to right) and then tries to produce as short edges as possible and as few edge overlaps as possible.</seg>
